            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Neutron flux was monitored by counting the recoil",
                "protons from a polyethylene foil. Accuracy of",
                "monitoring was better than 2%. Calibration of",
                "the monitor was based on the 847 keV gamma transition",
                "in Fe-56 from Fe-56(n,p)Mn-56 ,the cross section of",
                "which is 57 mb (D.C.Santry, Can.J.Phys.42,1030(64))"
              ]
